snippet.title: Goodboy Galaxy GBA early footage
snippet.description: We're still working hard on this project, here's a bit of footage from the first few planets (no bosses or big spoilers).  Sign up for updates on our site https://goodboygalaxy.com/ to be emailed when it's ready!
